ral\nanalysis will be interepreted for the smoothed-TV functional. The result of\nthis work is applicable for any strongly convex functional.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 17:12:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-17"}
