ions and the relative strengths of the underdamped and overdamped\ncontributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 21:12:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Apr 2016 13:09:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-05"}
