 low-mass cut-off, it\nreproduces observations over three decades in mass. We also rule out a low-mass\nstar dominated \"bottom-heavy\" IMF in a single star-forming region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 22:07:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2016 17:59:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-02"}
