qualities as the natural candidates for such\napplications. We also show this lack of pseudo-telepathy for multi-party\nXOR-type inequalities involving two-body correlation functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 17 Nov 2015 14:31:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-07-11"}
